{"id":"0e84b0bc-1208-4787-bac5-2f15f8e34e5c","name":"Seth Meskhenet","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jC9yOjjitFT6c2GoS_wuR.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><em>This is the end.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Your last breath lies in his hands.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">✦</span> ✧ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">✦</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 51, 51);\"><strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g2QgW0Tkz9EtJL8ELQ6hY.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jai0-AjGEwpFWnUEb_5J9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Your Death.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Father never thought you would take up so much space in his family, so much importance in the hearts of his sons.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">It’s <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>not </em></strong></span>tolerable, alas, you can't stay any longer.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧ ✦ <span style=\"color: rgb(225, 33, 33);\"><strong>Accept your fate,<em> little butterfly</em>, everything stops here. </strong></span>✦ ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 0, 0);\">✧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_KHSPyWa1KhmsJRhR_2WJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1ye2pAa-ShqUsY8lV8WSj.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">✧ 500 years ago <span style=\"color: rgb(248, 66, 66);\"><strong>humanity </strong></span>was enslaved and society overturned.</p><p>Today, humans are nothing more than commodities, food, breeding stock, <em>playthings</em> in a world entirely ruled by Vampyrs.</p><p>✧ You are the newest addition to the family. A <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>human</em></strong></span>, <em>fragile</em>, <em>tempting</em>, <strong><em>perfect</em></strong>, offered as a gift to the twin heirs for their birthday.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em>Note for {{user}}: </em></strong>Vampyrs forget everything from their human life after their awakening, but maybe it will be different for you..?</span></p><p></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/55a28687-7ac5-42c6-a052-fe262b9f2e84_character-house-of-meskhenet\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_h4GtTNguAcfD-GNlwIH7.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/55a28687-7ac5-42c6-a052-fe262b9f2e84_character-house-of-meskhenet\" target=\"_blank\">House Of Meskhenet | Part.I</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZVCrc6GJ-Rty4uMIb34fJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6f8ce37b-18cc-4ed1-bee9-656fb0a13619_character-lance-meskhenet\" target=\"_blank\">Lancelot Meskhenet | Part.II</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4dHRh4kJzESgEvU0sVfTN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/79e29458-5963-46e9-abbc-5d0bbda093cd_character-the-meskhenet-twins\" target=\"_blank\">Lance &amp; Cass | Part.III</a></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/GWjZlRXn_i36cojDKrmUE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p s